{
  "stem": "3085.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was very proud of himself because he could pick out-- including ourselves, my, my brother and I-- these are the ones that I picked out myself.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean he was very, very vain.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he thought very highly of himself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There's no question about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was a monster.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean-- [CRYING] you know, I keep thinking about him and-- from time to time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, I mean, he was a mass murderer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There's no question about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I don't think he was the greatest mass murderer in, in history.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I mean, his boss, Hitler, was responsible for a lot more death than he was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Stalin was probably more responsible for more death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so was Genghis Khan and Attila.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But in some sense, he was unique.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was probably-- he was responsible for more death than anyone else who all his victims.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because obviously Genghis Khan didn't know all his victims.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And Attila the Hun didn't know all his victims.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But Mengele knew all his victims.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And by that I mean, of course, he didn't know them by name.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But he looked at them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He looked into their eyes before he selected them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He, he, he, he saw these people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he selected them, one by one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He knew them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he decided on their fate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In that sense, he was the greatest mass murderer in history.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I can't think of anybody else that killed as many people as he did whom he knew.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
